---
import Layout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '@/components/ui/Button.astro';
import Card from '@/components/ui/Card.astro';
import Container from '@/components/layout/Container.astro';
import '@/styles/components/about-section.css';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="About Me | Dale Rogers">
  <main class="pt-32 md:pt-40">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <Container class="mb-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1
          class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-6"
        >
          About me
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-8">
          I'm a dreamer, designer, tinkerer and doer. I fell in love with service and strategic
          design because it is the place I can create impact.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-8">
          I dig into an idea to determine what is authentic, human, and relevant. Then I use all the
          tools of tech and design to bring it to life. To create a solution and design that is
          tangible, experiential, supportive and sustainable.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Service Design Philosophy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
            I believe that great service design happens at the intersection of human needs, business
            strategy, and technical possibility. Every service touchpoint is an opportunity to build
            trust, create value, and make someone's day a little better.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>

    <!-- Location Section -->
    <Container class="mb-24">
      <div class="bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2
            class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-6 text-center"
          >
            I'm in Canberra, Australia
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-8 text-center">
            But I'm not constrained by geography or time zones. Collaboration is key! I've helped
            organisations in Australia, and the US use the power of design to create a positive
            social impact with technology.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-3">
                Local Expertise
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Deep understanding of Australian government, education, and business contexts.
                Experience with local accessibility standards and regional requirements.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-3">
                Global Perspective
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
                International collaboration experience. Understanding of diverse cultural contexts
                and global service design best practices.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mt-8">
            <Button variant="primary" href="/contact">Get in touch</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <Container class="mb-24">
      <h2
        class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-12 text-center"
      >
        What I care about
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Collaboration builds quality
          </h3>
          <p class="text-grey-600 dark:text-grey-400">
            Every day, I practice genuine collaboration, building on one another's concepts and
            sketches until it's impossible to say where the idea came from in the first place.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Push a little further
          </h3>
          <p class="text-grey-600 dark:text-grey-400">
            I constantly push boundaries, challenge standards, and redefine what's possible. Yes,
            that makes my job a lot of work, but it's also what makes it so worthwhile.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Be good to work with
          </h3>
          <p class="text-grey-600 dark:text-grey-400">
            Be nice. Be optimistic. Be supportive. Treat tough problems as interesting challenges.
            Be critical, not cynical. That's the attitude I bring to my work every day.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Details make the difference
          </h3>
          <p class="text-grey-600 dark:text-grey-400">
            I care about all the little things, the stuff no one else will notice, because that
            meticulous commitment to excellence is exactly what sets me apart.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Work with only the brightest
          </h3>
          <p class="text-grey-600 dark:text-grey-400">
            In my collaborators, partners, and clients, I seek out people who take pride in their
            work and genuinely excel at it.
          </p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary dark:text-primary mb-4">
            Always get it done
          </h3>
          <p class="text-grey-600 dark:text-grey-400">
            When I say I'll deliver, I do. When Plan A doesn't work, I don't make excuses I start
            executing Plan B. You won't see me in a suit very often, but my work ethic is 100%
            professional.
          </p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </Container>

    <!-- Service Design Approach Section -->
    <Container class="mb-24">
      <div class="bg-primary dark:bg-primary text-primary-contrast rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6 text-center">
          My Service Design Approach
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="bg-white/20 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
            >
              <span class="text-2xl">üîç</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Research & Discovery</h3>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-90">
              Deep user research, stakeholder mapping, and service ecosystem analysis
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="bg-white/20 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
            >
              <span class="text-2xl">üéØ</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Strategy & Design</h3>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-90">
              Service blueprints, journey mapping, and strategic service architecture
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div
              class="bg-white/20 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"
            >
              <span class="text-2xl">üöÄ</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Implementation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-90">
              Prototyping, testing, and building organisational capacity for ongoing improvement
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <Container class="mb-24">
      <div class="bg-grey-900 dark:bg-grey-800 text-primary rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6">Ready to collaborate?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Let's work together to create impactful solutions that transform how your organisation
          delivers value.
        </p>
        <Button variant="primary" href="/contact">
          Start a conversation
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            fill="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </Button>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </main>
</Layout>
